&lt;li&gt;Work across service boundaries, own critical architecture/service design, and help evolve Tubi&#39;s backend system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Background:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Elixir or strong background in other backend or functional programming languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with gRPC/Protocol Buffers, RESTful API design, Kubernetes, and observability solutions&lt;/li&gt;
