&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated and proactive individual who is ready to become a part of&amp;nbsp;the CTV industry and grow their experience with Tubi. This person will work closely with&amp;nbsp;seasoned Account Managers to support their day-to-day client-facing and internal&amp;nbsp;responsibilities. The Account Management team ensures the day-to-day success of our clients by managing the campaign process from start to finish, leveraging strategic insights and our proprietary tools to deliver campaigns effectively. In this role, you will have the opportunity to&amp;nbsp;learn the fundamentals of account management at Tubi, learn about the growing CTV space,&amp;nbsp;and become an expert in Tubi products and services. This role will also provide exposure to&amp;nbsp;media planning and strategy, supporting cross-functional teams in developing and executing&amp;nbsp;client campaigns.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This is a hybrid role based out of our New York City office. You must be willing to travel to our New York City office four days/week.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the day-to-day functions of account management, including internal and external reporting, client presentations, monitoring ad campaign performance, and campaign optimizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Account Management to learn Tubi products and service offerings, and how they translate into effective campaign strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in Sales and Account Management meetings to understand client objectives, campaign strategies, and planning considerations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Media Strategy and cross-functional teams to support the development of media plans, including audience targeting, channel recommendations, and campaign setup&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in campaign forecasting, pacing, and performance tracking to ensure delivery against client goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Ad Operations to help launch campaigns and monitor delivery; develop a foundational understanding of campaign management and optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the creation and maintenance of planning materials such as media plans, flowcharts, and campaign documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with third-party measurement and reporting tools to analyze performance and identify optimization opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
